WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.420 --> 00:00:15.960
Grif, just remain calm, okay?

00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:20.240
Calm?! I'm surrounded by aliens and I think they're trying to kill me.

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:22.180
They're definitely trying to kill me.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.960
Grif, do you know where Simmons is? Grif?

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:27.840
Hello?
- Oh god! I don't wanna die!

00:00:28.060 --> 00:00:29.040
You'll die!

00:00:30.380 --> 00:00:32.720
Sounds like your buddy wandered into a firefight mode.

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:33.740
What's that?

00:00:33.740 --> 00:00:36.220
He has to fight wave after wave of aliens till it's over.

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:38.220
When is it over?
- When he dies.

00:00:38.220 --> 00:00:41.940
Hmm, well that's not so good, on the plus side, though it shouldn't take too long.

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:45.360
Hey, let him know if he pre-ordered from Gamestop and get some new armor.

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:48.160
Uh, not sure he stands a chance either way.

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:51.780
Well, he could find his way to multiplayer, he could enter a one versus one tournament.

00:00:51.780 --> 00:00:53.840
He has to be one of the ones.

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:56.200
Yeah.
- It seems like a bad idea for him.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:58.800
Well, they have prizes for four versus four tournaments too.

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:01.760
You got any four versus three and a half compitition?

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:04.520
No.
- Then he probably wouldn't qualify.

