♪ This map is so freakin' huge I'm kind of freaked out ♪

00:01:53.860 --> 00:01:58.100
♪ Forge World is so big! ♪

00:02:00.340 --> 00:02:01.500
♪ Halo Reach ♪

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:07.300
Oh brother, finally.

00:02:07.300 --> 00:02:08.860
Hey, what's up Sarge?
- Grif...!

00:02:08.860 --> 00:02:11.820
You made it!
- Barely, those aliens never seem to stop.

00:02:11.820 --> 00:02:14.240
So eventually, I just played dead and they left.

00:02:14.240 --> 00:02:15.940
Then I fell asleep for a few hours.

00:02:15.940 --> 00:02:17.980
Playing dead is more work than I'm used to.

00:02:17.980 --> 00:02:21.160
Where have you guys been?
-  I got stuck all the way across the map.

00:02:21.220 --> 00:02:22.680
This place is huge!

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:24.640
And I got attacked by a bunch of aliens.

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:26.520
At least you had to win some prizes.

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:29.280
I've been trying to hold the Blues by myself.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.760
Simmons, why are they shooting at each other?

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:36.120
Oh, I told them if they didn't attacked us, I would trade them my pre-order code for the exclusive chest piece.

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:37.760
Now they're fighting each other to see who gets it.

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:39.980
Bar code!
- But you already used your code,

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:41.140
...you're wearing it.

00:02:41.300 --> 00:02:42.300
Yeah, but don't know that.

00:02:42.300 --> 00:02:46.800
See fellas, I guess my plan worked after all. Now let's get ready for Reach!

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.360
And I'm gonna take a nap first.

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:53.500
Oh you can't, the delivery guy stopped by, you won one of the Noble Team statues. It takes up your whole bunk.

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:55.240
Whoa! This thing is huge!

